  "title": "secretx umbrella: re-export WriteableSecretStore and add from_uri_writable",
  "description": "Two changes in secretx/src/lib.rs:\n1. Add WriteableSecretStore to the pub use secretx_core::{...} re-export list.\n2. Add from_uri_writable(uri: &str) -> Result<Arc<dyn WriteableSecretStore>, SecretError>. The function mirrors from_uri: parse URI, match on backend(), dispatch to the 9 writable backends casting to Arc<dyn WriteableSecretStore>, return InvalidUri for env/bitwarden and for signing-only backends (aws-kms, local-signing, wolfhsm). AWS SM with ?field= query param: return InvalidUri with message 'aws-sm with ?field= selector is read-only; remove ?field= to use from_uri_writable' to catch the footgun at construction time.",
